intellimate.izou.output

Class OutputExtension<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • intellimate.izou.output.OutputExtension<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable, java.util.concurrent.Callable<T>

    public abstract class OutputExtension<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Callable<T>, Identifiable
    OutputExtension's purpose is to take resourceData and convert it into another data format so that it can be rendered correctly by the output-plugin. These objects are represented in the form of future objects that are stored in tDoneList
